a de Queixeiro]] |[[Ría de Betanzos]] |[[Monfero]], [[Vilarmaior]], [[Miño, A Coruña|Miño]] |[[La Coruña (province)|A Coruña]] |- |[[Bazar (river)|Bazar]] | |[[Xallas]] | |[[La Coruña (province)|A Coruña]] |- |[[Beba (river)|Beba]] | |[[Xallas]] | |[[La Coruña (province)|A Coruña]] |- |[[Belelle]] |[[Monte Fontardión]] |[[Ría de Ferrol]] |[[A Capela]], [[Cabanas, Galicia|Cabanas]], [[Fene]], [[Neda, Galicia|Neda]] |[[La Coruña (province)|A Coruña]] |- |[[Beloi]] | | | |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[Beluso]] |[[Monte Muralla]], [[Lousame]] |[[Ría de Arousa]] |[[Lousame]], [[Boiro]] |[[La Coruña (province)|A Coruña]] |- |[[Bermaña]] | |[[Umia]] |[[Caldas de Reis]] |[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]] |- |[[Bertón]] | |[[Anllóns]] | |[[La Coruña (province)|A Coruña]] |- |[[Bexa (river)|Bexa]] | |[[Te(river)|Te]] | |[[La Coruña (province)|A Coruña]] |- |[[Bibei]] |[[Pico do Moncalvo]], [[Provincia de Zamora|Zamora]] |[[Sil (river)|Sil]] |[[Porto, Zamora|Porto]], [[Viana do Bolo]], [[O Bolo]], [[Manzaneda]], [[A Pobra de Trives]], [[Ribas de Sil]], [[Quiroga, Galicia|Quiroga]] |[[Ourense (province)|Ourense]] |- |[[Blanqueño]] | |[[Parga (river)|Parga]] | |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[Boedo, río Parga|Boedo]] | |[[Parga (river)|Parga]] | |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[de Bois]] | |[[dos Gafos]] | |[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]] |- |[[Bolaños (river)|Bolaños]] |[[Lagostelle, Guitiriz]] |[[Parga (river)|Parga]] |[[Guitiriz]] |[[La Coruña (province)|A Coruña]] |- |[[Rego da Bordeseca]] | |[[Calvar]] | |[[La Coruña (province)|A Coruña]] |- |[[Rego de Borela]] | |[[Almofrei]] | |[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]] |- |[[Bouzas]] | |[[Anllóns]] | |[[La Coruña (province)|A Coruña]] |- |[[Brandeso]] | |[[Iso (river)|Iso]] | |[[La Coruña (province)|A Coruña]] |- |[[Brantega]] | |[[Arnego]] | |[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]] |- |[[Brea (river)|Brea]] | | | |[[La Coruña (province)|A Coruña]] |- |[[Brexa]] | |[[Mero (river)|Mero]] | |[[La Coruña (province)|A Coruña]]