rina, Santiago de Compostela]] |[[Sar (river)|Sar]] |[[Santiago de Compostela]] |[[La Coruña (province)|A Coruña]] |- |[[Sarria (river)|Sarria]] |[[Triacastela]] |Neira |[[Triacastela]], [[Samos]], [[Sarria]], [[O Páramo]], [[Láncara]] |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[Saviñao]] | | | |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[Selmo]] | |[[Sil (river)|Sil]] | |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[Ser (river)|Ser]] |[[Donís, Cervantes]] |[[Navia (river)|Navia]] |[[Cervantes]], [[Navia de Suarna]], [[Becerreá]] |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[Sil (river)|Sil]] |[[La Cueta, León]] |[[Minho (river)|Minho]] |[[Laciana]], [[O Bierzo]], [[Ourense (province)]] |[[Provincia de León|León]], |[[Ourense (province)|Ourense]], [[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[Sinto (river)|Sinto]] | |[[Masma]] | |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[Rego Sobrecín]] |[[Óutara, A Pobra do Brollón]] |[[Cabe (river)|Cabe]] | |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[Soldón]] |[[Serra dos Cabalos]], [[Quiroga, Galicia|Quiroga]] |[[Sil (river)|Sil]] |[[Quiroga, Galicia|Quiroga]] |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[Sor Mañón|Sor]] |[[Muras, Galicia|Muras]], [[Ourol]] |Ría do [[O Barqueiro|Barqueiro]] |[[Mañón]], [[Muras, Galicia|Muras]], [[Ourol]], [[O Vicedo]] |[[La Coruña (province)|A Coruña]], [[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[Suarna]] |[[Fonsagrada]] |[[Navia (river)|Navia]] | |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |-
