a]] |- |[[Tenorio (river)|Tenorio]] |[[Monte Tenorio]], [[Cotobade]] |[[Lérez, ría de Pontevedra|Lérez]] |[[Cotobade]] |[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]] |- |[[Termes (river)|Termes]] |[[Empiade, Cerdeira, As Neves]] |[[Minho (river)|Minho]] |[[As Neves]] |[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]] |- |[[Tines (river)|Tines]] |[[Mazaricos]] |[[Ría de Muros e Noia]] |[[Mazaricos]], [[Outes]] |[[La Coruña (province)|A Coruña]] |- |[[Tolda]] | |[[Boedo, río Parga|Boedo]] | |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[Torneiros]] | |[[Azúmara]] | |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[Toxa]] |[[Forcarei]] |[[O Deza]] |[[Forcarei]], [[Silleda]] |[[Pontevedra (province)|Pontevedra]] |- |[[Traba (river)|Traba]] |[[Lousame]] |[[Ría de Muros e Noia]] |[[Lousame]], [[Noia]] |[[La Coruña (province)|A Coruña]] |- |[[Trabada (river)|Trabada]] | |[[Eo (river)|Eo]] | |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[Regato Trasadehesa]] | |[[Antiga]] | |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[Tras da Serra]] |[[Alto de San Xoán]], [[Ribeira, Ambosores]] |[[Sor Mañón|Sor]] | |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[Rego de Tras das Penas]] |[[San Pedro do Incio, O Incio]] |[[Cabe (river)|Cabe]] | |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[Trimaz]] | |[[Ladra (river)|Ladra]] | |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[Tronceda]] |[[Serra do Xistral]] |[[Masma]] |[[Mondoñedo]] |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |- |[[Tuño]] | |[[Arnoia]] | |[[Ourense (province)|Ourense]] |- |[[Turía (river)|Turía]] | |[[Eo (river)|Eo]] | |[[Lugo (province)|Lugo]] |-
